    "title": "Distribution Manager Vacancy at Ecom Express - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Ecom Express. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Distribution Manager to strengthen our Meerut-based team.\n\nAbout Ecom Express:\nEcom Express is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ecom Express!",
